TextEng: I want to ask you some questions.
Me got question for you.
I should go now.
Me want go now.
Who are you?
Who you be?
What is this place? How does this world exist inside a snow globe?
Text: 여긴 어디죠? 이 세계가 스노 글로브 안에 어떻게 존재하는 거예요?

TextEng: What be this place? How it be inside snowball?
Text: 여기 어디야? 어떻게 스노우볼 안에 있어?

TextEng: Can you tell me anything about the dwarves and dryads?
Text: 드워프와 드라이어드에 대해 뭔가 말해주실 수 있나요?

TextEng: Me want know more 'bout dwarf and dryad.
Text: 나 드워프랑 드라이어드 더 알고 싶어.

TextEng: I am <FullName>. I am searching for the Words of Power.
Me am <FullName>. Me look for Power Word.
Text: 나 <FullName>이야. 나 권능의 언령 찾고 있어.

TextEng: I'm here to kill you, wyrm!
Me want kill you, dragon!
May I ask you some questions?
It okay if me ask you some questions?
Enough talking, coward! Time to die!
No more talk! You die now, coward!
Yes. Tell me about the Word of Power.
Yes. Me want you tell me 'bout Word of Power.
I want to ask you something else.
Me want ask you something else.
Do you know anything about a Word of Power?
Text: 권능의 언령에 대해 아시는 게 있나요?

TextEng: You know stuff 'bout Power Word?
Can you tell me anything about this amulet?
Text: 이 호신부에 대해 뭔가 말해주실 수 있나요?

TextEng: You know stuff 'bout this amulet?
How did you end up inside this snowglobe?
Text: 어떻게 이 스노 글로브 안에 들어가게 됐나요?

TextEng: How you end up inside snowball?
Why are they always fighting each other?
Why creatures be always fighting each other?
What was that about the Word of Power?
You say something 'bout Power Word?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> You seem quite upset about this amulet. Is there something about it you're not telling me?
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 이 호신부에 대해 꽤 화가 나신 것 같은데요. 제게 말하지 않은 뭔가가 있나요?

TextEng: Artifact?
Where is the Word now?
Where be Word now?
What if I just take it from you?
Maybe me just take Power Word from you?
Give me the Word or die!
You give Word or you die!
Is there nothing I can offer in exchange for the Word?
Text: 언령과 교환할 수 있는 게 정말 없나요?

TextEng: There not be nothing you want in trade for Power Word?
Text: 권능의 언령이랑 바꿀 거 정말 없어?

TextEng: It's wrong to enslave these creatures!
Text: 이 생명체들을 노예로 만드는 건 잘못된 일입니다!

TextEng: It be wrong to make them be you slave!
